reviewText: The problem this DVD is not the quality of the film transfer but the huge fact the the last 10 minutes of this film is not on the DVD. So you in essence have no ending.

For what it's worth (watching it with my cousin with blankets pulled over our heads around 1962) it is terrific.  Everything a 50s b-horror film needs, somewhat cheesy effects, evil Nazis, exploding volcanos and lots of sexy girls who somehow manage tops on this desert island that make their boobs look like Pontiac tail-fins and compliments Jayne Mansfield make-up and hair-dos.  Acting is about what you'd expect.  Still fun.
Great movie, but the ending is cut off. Disappointing.

The ending of the movie gets cut off. It wasn't too bad but you don't get to see the ending

This is a great old sci fi movie but the end is cut off.  The actors did a great job with the script although the make-up was a little cheezy.  The end would be happy as most of these 50's flicks were so I don't think much is missing.  If you need the whole movie don't rent it.
